title: Sandusky Lee CA41361872-05 Welded Steel Classic Storage Cabinet 4 Adjustable Shelves Locking
description:
Welded steel storage cabinet with four adjustable shelves two hinged doors and a locking swing handle is suitable for organizing storing and securing items
Swing handle has a lock and three-point locking system for security
Shelves adjust in 2 increments to accommodate items of varying heights
Powder coat finish for resistance to chipping and corrosion
Cabinet ships assembled handle and lock assembly required instructions included tools for assembly not included
